A '''Dothraki crone''' is an unnamed minor character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. She is played by guest star [[Amira Ghazella]] and only appears in &quot;[[A Golden Crown]].&quot; She is a member of the ''[[dosh khaleen]]'', the widows of deceased ''[[Khal|khals]]'' who preside over [[Dothraki]] religious rituals.
